Hey There, and welcome to Limelight!

We're glad you've decided to join! Here are a few tips to get you started.

1. Follow some topics
Go find stuff you're interested in! Then follow it and have related posts show up in your feed.

2. Contribute
Find something cool on the web you want to share? That's what Limelight is for! Just click "Contribute" up top!

3. Check back often
Posts are constantly being submitted, allowing you to get the lastest on all your favorite topics.

4. Use the tutorials
Click "Tutorials" on the bottom left after logging in. There's tons of info on how to use the site.

If you want to find out more about how it all works, log in and click Tutorials on the bottom left.